#. type: Fenced code block (html)
#: docs/8.x/blade.md:1215 docs/master/blade.md:1156
#, no-wrap
msgid "@push('scripts')\n"
"    This will be second...\n"
"@endpush\n\n"
"// Later...\n\n"
"@prepend('scripts')\n"
