#. type: Plain text
#: docs/8.x/cashier-paddle.md:258 docs/master/cashier-paddle.md:218
#, no-wrap
msgid "    <x-paddle-checkout :override=\"$payLink\" class=\"w-full\" height=\"500\" />\n"
