#. type: Plain text
#: docs/8.x/cashier-paddle.md:1125 docs/master/cashier-paddle.md:1085
#, no-wrap
msgid "    $lastPayment = $subscription->lastPayment();\n"
"    $nextPayment = $subscription->nextPayment();\n"
