#. type: Plain text
#: docs/8.x/cashier-paddle.md:1129 docs/master/cashier-paddle.md:1089
#, no-wrap
msgid "    Next payment: {{ $nextPayment->amount() }} due on {{ $nextPayment->date()->format('d/m/Y') }}\n"
