#. type: Plain text
#: docs/8.x/horizon.md:193 docs/8.x/queues.md:1487 docs/master/horizon.md:193
#: docs/master/queues.md:1425
#, no-wrap
msgid "<a name=\"installing-supervisor\"></a>\n"
