#: docs/8.x/notifications.md:1077 docs/master/notifications.md:1049
#, no-wrap
msgid "    /**\n"
"     * Get the Slack representation of the notification.\n"
"     *\n"
"     * @param  mixed  $notifiable\n"
"     * @return SlackMessage\n"
